snippet.title: Live Coding: Mobile App w/ Flutter
snippet.description:
Flutter is a framework for making native cross-platform mobile apps with the Dart programming language. Last night we looked at the Dart language itself. Tonight, let's check out Flutter and try to make a mobile app!

GitHub: https://www.github.com/DevDungeon
